1. Ja otkrijem tajnu o uspehu. (I uncover the secret to success.)
2. Ona će otkriti istinu svom prijatelju. (She will reveal the truth to her friend.)
3. Ti si otkrio svoje talente. (You have discovered your talents.)
4. *Otkrivam* da sam pogrešio. (I admit that I was wrong.)
5. Njegova radoznalost ga je *otkrila*. (His curiosity exposed him.)
6. Oni su nam *otkrili* svoje planove. (They revealed their plans to us.)
7. Kada su *otkrili* da su ostali bez goriva, bili su u problemu. (When they discovered they were out of fuel, they were in trouble.)
8. *Otkrivaš* se kao osoba koja je spremna da pomogne drugima. (You reveal yourself as a person who is willing to help others.)
9. Ona je bila iznenađena kada joj je *otkriveno* da je dobila nagradu. (She was surprised when she was revealed to have won the prize.)
10. Da li ćeš *otkriti* svoje planove za budućnost? (Will you reveal your plans for the future?)